Package jzombies

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Connection
    This is an interface that helps to make the connection between the agents.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Agent
    This class represents the base for all the agents; user, defender, and attacker.
    Attacker
    This class is a subclass of Agent class that represents an attacker who sends malicious requests to the defender
    Defender
    This class is a subclass of Agent class that represents a defender who receives the request from user and attacker, and verifies request against the security policies and take the appropriate action.
    Human  
    JZombiesBuilder  
    Request
    This class is a simple TCP request
    User
    This class is a subclass of Agent class that represents a user who sends normal requests to the defender
    Zombie
